{"tid":370561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門大停電港人被困酒店 賭廳水浸市民街頭游水","createTime":"2017-08-23T06:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T08:25:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ca039b3f136951b6706adb8630f4c3ecbc11d8","tid":370561,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503467647_7e3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503467647_7e3f.jpg&h=8603c71c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 受天鴿影響，澳門多區出現水浸，今早11時起更突然停電。其中在氹仔剛開業不久的羅斯福酒店，至中午約12時，酒店突然停電，房間內的燈光、冷氣及電話，甚至公共地方的升降機全部停止運作。有原本在酒店慶生的港人遊客表示，酒店內的住客立即走到走廊查詢，但職員指「個風太勁，所有嘢都停哂」，連酒店的餐廳都停止供應膳食，全部客人被困酒店。由於酒店不少房間有露店，雨水由露台的門隙湧入，客人慌忙用毛巾處理。酒店職員更着客人遠離露台，走出走廊較為安全。<br />\n<br />\n澳電表示，由於部分地區供電設備被水浸，內港一帶發生停電事故，直至中午珠海供電出現故障，本澳八成以上電力由內地輸澳，導致全澳廣泛地區大停電。部份銀行被逼暫停營業，有食肆亦要關門。多區出現水浸，有市民被逼在街頭泳水，網上亦流傳有賭廳水浸的照片。澳門電台報道，澳門及離島有多宗困升降機事故，消防正在加緊救援。澳門中區及北區多處交通燈因停電而停止運作，政府呼籲駕駛者留意現場警員指揮。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170823/57116743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170823%2F57116743&d=upHURH%2BY6M7wXchtIaTU5b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=dd8cb9a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170823%2F57116743&h=b4d77c03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170823/57116743</a>"},{"pid":"1471d0557c23c51394522167c9766672d9358686","tid":370561,"uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503467085_9275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503467085_9275.jpg&h=61ab2496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n酒店窗邊有大量雨水滲入，住客要用毛巾塞着。（本報記者攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503467649_ea59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503467649_ea59.jpg&h=aac097d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170823/large/1503467087_2199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170823%2Flarge%2F1503467087_2199.jpg&h=568c6347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有澳門酒店停電，住客被困無法離開。（本報記者攝）"},{"pid":"f6b1786c3da99770f8efb54e2afca470bc11c5de","tid":370561,"uid":62010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"2f199d2e7e1c3b79fd278f2049416afd4b6d5048","tid":370561,"uid":78671,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:08:07.000Z","msg":"快點去趁亂偷碼吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db33288521d949424ca15591d23bec0678511b63","tid":370561,"uid":23170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[住客立即走到走廊查詢，但職員指「個風太勁，所有嘢都停哂」，連酒店的餐廳都停止供應膳食，全部客人被困酒店。由於酒店不少<span style=\"color: red;\">房間有露店</span>，雨水由露台的門隙湧入，客人慌忙用毛巾處理。酒店職員更着客人遠離露台，走出走廊較為安全。<br />\n<br />\n]</blockquote><br />\n乜鳩嘢叫露店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8eff86d52dc969e5e779198fb83f1c11b81c99b","tid":370561,"uid":37661,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"幫支那買電，抵撚死。"},{"pid":"cfaa9ed6e27bf9f704e0e033f703db88354b2509","tid":370561,"uid":48360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"我親戚係澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d9cf92c6